There may be software errors in 'Horny' as there may be in any software. Inutilis Software and the author, Timo Kloss, do not accept liability for any damage  caused by using 'Horny'. All reasonable efforts will be made to rectify any problems reported in 'Horny'.


PERMITTED USE OF HORNY SOFTWARE

You are permitted to use 'Horny Lite' without charge or registration. To use the full version of 'Horny' (i.e., not 'Horny Lite') it is necessary to register at Inutilis Software and pay for a registration key.

A separate registration key must be purchased for each computer on which the full version of 'Horny' is run. 

Decompilation of any Horny binary files to source code is prohibited.

